ackground": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/664116220"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIweuPnOHGxKIZEAMaCTEwOTg1OTAzMyCihOi1BjAAOKkDQBlyCTY2NDExNjIyMHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "26_1723486422.181817", "card_id": "Q_664081861", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 94}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "外交部回应乌军进入俄领土「呼吁各方遵守局势降温『三原则』」，目前俄乌局势如何？下一阶段会怎么走？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "问：据报道，乌克兰军队近日攻入俄罗斯本土库尔斯克州。俄方称乌军袭击已造成 60 多名平民伤亡，俄军已遏止乌军进攻，库尔斯克州宣布进入紧急状态。乌总统泽连斯基发表讲话称，俄将战争带到乌领土，现在应感受到其行为的后果。美方称，美事先不掌握乌军本次进攻计划，乌此举不是升级行为，只是争取胜利的必要之举。美允许乌使用美制武器回击来自俄边境的袭击，乌军此次行动符合这一情况。中方对此有何评论？ 答：中方注意到有关情况。中方在乌克兰问题上的立场是一贯的、明确的，呼吁各方遵守局势降温「三原则」，即战场不外溢、战事不升级、各方不拱火。中方将继续同国际社会保持沟通，为推动危机政治解决发挥建设性作用。外交部回应乌军进入俄领土：呼吁各方遵守局势降温「三原则」 (thepaper.cn)"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-f298947066f44741567c2a5d626a976b_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "43 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/664081861"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIweuPnOHGxKIZEAMaCTEwOTg1MTM2NSDroea1BjAAOKABQBpyCTY2NDA4MTg2MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1723486422.182367", "card_id": "Q_663719157", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 70}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待《黑神话：悟空》正式完工，8 月 20 号全球同步上市？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-7d3190df18f7b9a11cd9625abc37ee07_1440w.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "38 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/663719157"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IweuPnOHGxKIZEAMaCTEwOTc3MDg3NSDfzM+1BjAAOHVAG3IJNjYzNzE5MTU3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1723486422.182570", "card_id": "Q_660643005", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 36}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有哪些描写秋天的古典诗词？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-f01294eb2ef54b7ffaa80bcfe26a5e74_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "38 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/660643005"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IweuPnOHGxKIZEAMaCTEwOTA4NzIyMiD/z5S0BjAAOD1AHHIJNjYwNjQzMDA1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1723486422.182755", "card_id": "Q_664070386", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 173}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "网传别克撞上柯尼塞格定损 406 万，车主辟谣「定损结果没出，不会为难对方」，哪些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，浙江宁波的一辆别克车撞上一辆超级跑车柯尼塞格，引发广泛关注。 随后，有网传消息称，这辆被撞的柯尼塞格是「沙特龙的车，4700 万元」，「最后定损 406 万元，保险出 300 万元，别克女车主出 106 万元，车运回瑞典修」。 科尼赛格品牌是由克里斯·冯·科尼赛格创立于 1994 年，总部设立在瑞典南部的恩厄尔霍尔姆。它主要生产超级跑车，规模不大，属于小型的超级跑车品牌。 红星新闻了解到，这辆柯尼塞格的车主网名叫「沙特龙」。8 月 11 日晚，沙特龙的一位朋友、博主「海派大叔」对红星新闻表示，网传消息均不实。 海派大叔介绍，事故发生在 8 月 10 日晚上，七夕节那天，沙特龙去找他弟弟喝咖啡，正常开着，被一位女士撞了。「车撞完后留给助理处理，他就走了。目前定损结果还没出，他也不会过于为难车主。」 来源：红星新闻别克撞上 4700 万柯尼塞格，定损 406 万？车主回应：定损结果没出，不会为难对方"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-4fc2934744b8c4b46d97a0b881353526_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "38 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/664070386"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIweuPnOHGxKIZEAMaCTEwOTg0ODg0OSDwzOW1BjAAOOACQB1yCTY2NDA3MDM4NngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": false, "next": "", "previous": "", "totals": 0}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "display_firs